franklin is located at 39deg29'23''n 86deg3'24''w / 39.48972degn 86.05667degw / 39.48972; -86.05667 (39.489585, -86.056784), 20 miles (32 km) south of polis and 90 miles (140 km) north of louisville, kentucky, on i-65 and u.s. 31. according to the united states census bureau, the city has a total area of 11.3 square miles (29 km2), all of it land.